Summary: UFO found on pictures taken at 5:50 A.M. that was not visible to the naked eye.
divs: Sighting DetailsWitness reports that he was taking pictures of the sunrise pn August 7, 2011 at 5:50 A.M. He reports that he took a fe pictures and did not see anything unusual in the sky. He reports that when he was downloading the pictures into his computer's "My Pictures Computer Library" he found picutes of the object on his pictures on the computer. He reports that he did not see the objects when he took the pictures. This report is being made for the witness by Fred Saluga, Chief Investigator for the State of West Virginia as witness does not want to be identified.
